5Ô∏è‚É£ **Infrastructure Testing**: Infra as Code enables the implementation of infrastructure testing practices. 
By writing tests for your infrastructure code, you can verify that your infrastructure meets the desired state, 
ensuring stability and reducing risks.

üåü Infra as Code, supported by tools like Ansible, brings the benefits of automation, consistency, scalability, and collaboration to 
infrastructure management. By treating infrastructure configurations as code, DevOps engineers can efficiently manage and evolve their
infrastructure in a controlled and predictable manner.
